description:
Bobby has a story written about him in the Arkansas Democrat-Gazette that revealed things he’s never talked about before. We draft our favorite movies that make you happy! Plus, we talk to Jenn Wayne of Runaway June about getting coronavirus waiting in line at the grocery store.
